{
  "texts": [
    "The results also imply that students can benefit from additional guidance training about AI literacy and effective prompt writing skills.",
    "Moreover, the association between AI interaction profiles and student performance might indicate the importance of promoting active and critical engagement with AI tools.",
    "Students who use ChatGPT for refining and improving their work, rather than solely for generation, tend to achieve better performance outcomes.",
    "Finally, the dynamic nature of students' AI interaction profiles over time suggests that ongoing support and adaptive strategies are crucial for maximizing the educational benefits of AI integration.",
    "The findings indicate diverse levels of reliance on ChatGPT among students, with a significant portion initially preferring to work independently."
  ]
}